videos.description: South Carolina isn't able to convert in the final seconds of quadruple overtime as Alabama comes out on top with an upset.
videos.headline: South Carolina's last chances don't fall in quadruple overtime

videos.description: Sindarius Thornwell records 44 points and 21 rebounds for No. 19 South Carolina, but it is not enough as Alabama edges the Gamecocks 90-86 in quadruple overtime.
videos.headline: Alabama tops South Carolina in 4OT

videos.description: South Carolina coach Frank Martin says he practiced his players for too long and they were too tired for Tuesday's game against Alabama, a quadruple overtime loss.
